WEBVTT

00:00.840 --> 00:01.620
Hold it, sir.

00:01.650 --> 00:02.250
Hold it, hold it!

00:07.870 --> 00:10.000
Nobody's eating. They're just staring at each

00:10.000 --> 00:14.880
other. What you got in the truck?

00:15.120 --> 00:16.980
Got a pistol in the glove box.

00:17.190 --> 00:18.600
Got a rifle behind the seat.

00:21.620 --> 00:27.840
Get in the truck. Yeah.

00:45.500 --> 00:46.670
They're gone.

00:53.620 --> 00:56.860
I'm gonna need wallets, rings, watches on the

00:56.860 --> 00:57.970
fucking table.

00:58.360 --> 00:59.710
Open it, open it!

01:01.180 --> 01:02.200
Hands on the table!

01:02.200 --> 01:03.550
Don't you fucking move!

01:04.030 --> 01:06.820
Eyes front. That's right, that's right.

01:10.520 --> 01:11.810
He's back. The cowboys back.

01:41.640 --> 01:42.690
It's around the corner.

01:45.810 --> 01:47.070
You think that's going to save you, you

01:47.070 --> 01:48.690
fucking coward! I'll fucking kill her!

01:48.990 --> 01:50.130
I swear to God, I'll fucking do it!

01:50.160 --> 01:51.570
That's right. Then you won't have anybody to

01:51.570 --> 01:55.710
hide behind, will you? Party's almost over.

01:56.400 --> 02:00.030
You see it? I got it whenever you want.
